### Blogging API Test Requests

# @name Register
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Jane Doe",
    "email": "jane@example.com",
    "password": "mySecurePassword"
}

###

# @name Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "jane@example.com",
    "password": "mySecurePassword"
}

###

# @name CreatePost
# Replace {{token}} with the token from Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "title": "My First Architecture Post",
    "content": "Building APIs with the Controller-Service pattern is incredibly satisfying!",
    "imageUrl": "https://example.com/placeholder.jpg"
}

###

# @name GetFeed
GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts

###

# @name ToggleLike
# Replace {{postId}} with an actual post ID
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/posts/{{postId}}/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# @name AddComment
POST http://localhost:5000/api/posts/{{postId}}/comment
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "text": "This is a fantastic tutorial! Thanks for sharing."
}

###

# @name AddReply
# Replace {{commentId}} with an actual comment ID
POST http://localhost:5000/api/posts/{{postId}}/comment/{{commentId}}/reply
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "text": "I completely agree, the architecture makes so much sense!"
}
